  <section>
    <p>
      Real estate is one of the most valuable asset classes, yet it has remained
      inaccessible, illiquid, and complex for too many people.
      <strong>Xcavate</strong> is changing that.
    </p>

    <p>
      Through <strong>blockchain technology</strong> and
      <strong>asset tokenization</strong>, Xcavate makes ownership
      transparent, inclusive, and efficient.
    </p>

    <h2>Why Tokenized Real Estate Matters</h2>

    <p>
      Tokenization allows real estate to be divided into smaller digital units,
      enabling fractional ownership. This opens the door for a new generation
      of investors, removes unnecessary intermediaries, and brings liquidity
      to a traditionally rigid market.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Increased accessibility to real estate investment</li>
      <li>Transparent and secure ownership on the blockchain</li>
      <li>Global participation without traditional barriers</li>
      <li>Education-first approach for long-term adoption</li>
    </ul>

